reviews.text:
Negative 500 stars should be given and authorities should be called. While eating there, I found half a cockroach in my fried rice. By the time I saw the creature I already ate some of the rice. This is utterly insane. I showed the waiter this and they made me a new dish, which I left untouch. 

蟹肉炒飯有甴曱! 我仲要講啲咩。。。
有圖有真相。自己睇
Takes a while for them to serve dishes, but overall a great bargain if you want a late lunch that comes with a drink.

G最近店鋪內外新裝修格調也舒服,泰國菜式水準也 keep 得住 good .
不好吃·碗筷不乾淨·無冼拿上枱·叫佢換過·拿來放下隔離位·服務差·以後不會再來!
